duties_responsibilities.duty: Develop and execute comprehensive SEO strategies to improve client's online visibility and search engine ranking.
Conduct in-depth keyword research and analysis to identify opportunities for client SEO improvement.
Optimize website content and structure for better search engine performance and user experience.
Perform technical SEO audits to identify and resolve issues that impact website ranking and visibility.
Produce client-facing reports, recommendations, and presentations to communicate SEO results and insights.
Collaborate with cross-functional teams to align SEO strategies with overall digital marketing initiatives.

education_certification.credential: Bachelor’s degree in Business, Marketing, Advertising, Journalism, or Communications
